Package gameObject.animal.model

Class AnimalModel

java.lang.Object
gameObject.animal.model.AnimalModel
public class AnimalModel
extends java.lang.Object
The model (M in MVC pattern) of Animal.

It keeps all information about Animal including score, lives, status, ends and the highest position. It is only responsible for keeping the data of Animal and has no control of any other modules or components. The controllers of Animal will access to AnimalModel to get data of Animal.

    • score

      The score of Animal.

    • lives

      private int lives
      The lives left for Animal.

    • status

      private int status
      The current status of Animal.
      • 0 : alive
      • 1 : car death
      • 2 : water death
      • 3 : game over

    • ends

      private int ends
      The number of destinations Animal has got to.

    • highestPosition

      private double highestPosition
      It tracks the smallest y coordinate of Animal has reached. The highest position Animal has reached in each round from born place to one destination.

    • noMove

      private boolean noMove
      It indicates whether Animal can move. True if Animal can't move, false if Animal can move.

    • nextLevel

      public void nextLevel()
      Updates the status and number of ends of AnimalModel when player gets to next level.

    • reachEnd

      public void reachEnd()
      Increases the number of ends when Animal reaches empty destination in game scene.

      It checks if the game has ended (next level) after the increament of the number of ends.

    • reachWrongEnd

      public void reachWrongEnd()
      Decreases the number of ends if Animal reaches an old destination in game scene.

    • checkEnds

      public void checkEnds()
      Checks if the game is over.

      If Animals has got 5 correct ends or Animal runs out of lives, it sets the status of Animal to 3. If the condition is false, does nothing.

    • die

      public void die()
      Decreses the number of lives when Animal dies.

      Checks if the game is over after the decrement.
